{"tid":2253322,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過睇兩個牙醫但講法完全唔同","createTime":"2020-10-22T05:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T19:09:19.000Z","uid":54139,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e2398888a2bdac0c58df14111991b9a9d01145","tid":2253322,"uid":54139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"下排門牙之前杜過牙根，因為最近食凍野有時會痹，就去咗睇牙醫<br />\n<br />\n第一個牙醫話我杜咗嗰隻牙生牙瘡，咁就好嚴重整到隔離兩隻牙都要杜牙根，然後俾咗個專科list我打去預約<br />\n<br />\n第二間嘅牙醫就話完全冇事，唔需要整，話會痹只係敏感牙齒/生智慧齒影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗住再book第三間睇，有冇ching試過類似情況？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5083b80f3b700afaf4031ce36f78480e13f6dea","tid":2253322,"uid":55851,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲case要睇8-10個牙醫，用AI cross reference佢地嘅report再gen個result出嚟先準"},{"pid":"75b0c6720a5cff784d0bf13d8857bd6bcc2ee3b6","tid":2253322,"uid":36339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5083b80f3b700afaf4031ce36f78480e13f6dea","tid":2253322,"uid":55851,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲case要睇8-10個牙醫，用AI cross reference佢地嘅report再gen個result出嚟先準"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:35:25.000Z","msg":"ching識波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34637354986e55cf0a709a4ba5cfa1e23afc40c7","tid":2253322,"uid":54139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5083b80f3b700afaf4031ce36f78480e13f6dea","tid":2253322,"uid":55851,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲case要睇8-10個牙醫，用AI cross reference佢地嘅report再gen個result出嚟先準"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"Ching學生邊有咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e77bce262dd0ff0d9a5e79af091831ddd56128","tid":2253322,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-