"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"有，<br />\n但醫生就話睇x光係完全冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBook咗專科11月中睇，當買個安心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"同埋牙嘅嘢 <br />\n我覺得唔好諗住一了百了<br />\n睇完無事，都只係暫時無事<br />\n你本身都係點都有啲嘢，先唔舒服 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一唔對路唔好拖<br />\n即刻約<br />\n<br />\n一個唔得<br />\n好似今次咁就即刻搵第個 <br />\n雖然咁睇都幾煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：掉以輕心過<br />\n<br />\n祝：牙齒健康"},{"pid":"a6bfdfa5b50a3ed1aa25960ecef99719230ecbaf","tid":2253322,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34637354986e55cf0a709a4ba5cfa1e23afc40c7","tid":2253322,"uid":54139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5083b80f3b700afaf4031ce36f78480e13f6dea","tid":2253322,"uid":55851,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲case要睇8-10個牙醫，用AI cross reference佢地嘅report再gen個result出嚟先準"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"Ching學生邊有咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"咁你可以試吓平安好醫生online診症"},{"pid":"1aaaf56797656becac5a9aafdc3c8cc944011662","tid":2253322,"uid":23315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:59:59.000Z","msg":"試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有排大牙咬野痛，一個連鎖叫我杜牙根，一個老牌嘅話牙齒敏感，叫我用下敏感牙膏，最後用咗防敏感牙膏一排就無事"},{"pid":"c3eec45f13a27d1d3e2c36118dc049788d270502","tid":2253322,"uid":236931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:00:05.000Z","msg":"試過<br />\n之前隻大牙成日痛<br />\n第一個牙醫話隻牙無得救要拔牙<br />\n第二個牙醫話盡力睇吓救不救到先<br />\n最後喺第二個牙醫整杜牙根，補牙，同整牙套"},{"pid":"cd652b1676cb88435c5c0d267d6d30aacbe06796","tid":2253322,"uid":54139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2867a2c20f8754796dec5ac51431b919ecde6833","tid":2253322,"uid":251039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84207aae8f683a2706835ebf12444f81e440f8b0","tid":2253322,"uid":54139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0322193df2cf22e2872c9a7c638d2f00b0346ac2","tid":2253322,"uid":251039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"你有無睇第二個嗰陣同佢講第個嘅嘢 <br />\n我諗真係睇多個啦<br />\n講哂第一第二個講嘅嘢<br />\n問佢點睇，同埋解釋返點解<br />\n然後自己做決定啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"有，<br />\n但醫生就話睇x光係完全冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBook咗專科11月中睇，當買個安心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:54:10.000Z","msg":"咁第一個有無解釋<br />\n點解另外兩隻有問題？<br />\nx光你自己睇完覺得點？<br />\n啲牙醫應該會指張x光解釋你聽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:03:24.000Z","msg":"第一個係照局部X-ray，咁就真係好清楚睇到牙腳有陰影。佢話可能係一開始杜牙根個醫生手勢唔好，冇發現第二隻牙都有感染，然後一直冇整令到佢擴散咗。<br />\n<br />\n第二個係照全口，睇嗰時就冇曬d陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醫生話如果真係生牙瘡，敲牙嘅表面係會痛，但我係完全唔痛。同埋食凍熱嘢d牙都會唔舒服會痛，我就淨係食凍嘢先有時會痹，佢就話好大機會係敏感牙齒"},{"pid":"9bb79e776b28f8b9184c95eff516bbed0328d5fc","tid":2253322,"uid":98431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:07:05.000Z","msg":"有d仆街係咪都叫你杜或去專科 都係想收錢多<br />\n<br />\n揀多間做檢查都係幾百 好過一野比成皮"},{"pid":"6d5a8a69831753e745ad04f216773c9ae1dfc81a","tid":2253322,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb88d651045341c5962a553abab8b50d09de8e79","tid":2253322,"uid":791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5586ce1e9555d7956f0c010d7dbefb98acfab88d","tid":2253322,"uid":54139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba212d609111b3e2aca5a3f6c9d99d8b38b7955f","tid":2253322,"uid":300013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:38:38.000Z","msg":"學校牙科抵屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"就係冇所以先要出去睇<img src